@Server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Test WeatherForecast
GET {{Server_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Server Connection
GET {{Server_HostAddress}}/api/test?username=TestUser

###

### Get All Users
GET {{Server_HostAddress}}/api/users

###

### Register New User
POST {{Server_HostAddress}}/api/Register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "password123"
}